# Cursor Rules - Skills-Aware Agent Configuration

## Overview

This project uses Claude Skills stored in `~/.claude/skills/` to provide specialized capabilities. The agent should be aware of these skills and use them when appropriate.

## Skills Directory

**Location:** `~/.claude/skills/`

All skills are stored as directories containing `SKILL.md` files with detailed instructions, workflows, and examples.

